metatags.name: Warren, Rick
metatags.summary:
The Rev. Rick Warren has created one of the most popular ministries in the country, based at the Saddleback Church in Orange County, Calif. Much of his message has reached an even broader audience outside of his mega-church through his best-selling faith-based book The Purpose-Driven Life.

In December 2008, Barack Obama chose Mr. Warren to deliver the invocation at his inauguration, making the pastor a lightning rod for controversy because of his outspoken opposition to abortion and same-sex marriage.
